        <p>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
<li>
    Stevan Stojanović Mokranjac (January 9, 1856–1914) was a Serbian composer and music educator.</li>
     <li>His work was essential in bringing the spirit of Valach Serbian unwritten folk poems into organized art. </p>
</li>
</div>
</body>
